<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Welcome to SAML Provider</title>
    <style>
        /* General body styling */
        body {
            font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f0f2f5;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            height: 100vh;
            color: #333;
        }

        /* Container for the landing page */
        .landing-container {
            background-color: #fff;
            padding: 60px;
            border-radius: 15px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            text-align: center;
            max-width: 600px;
            width: 100%;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        /* Logo styling */
        .logo {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .logo img {
            max-width: 100px;
            height: auto;
        }

        /* Heading styles */
        h1 {
            font-size: 2.8rem;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            color: #2c3e50;
        }

        h2 {
            font-size: 1.6rem;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            color: #7f8c8d;
        }

        /* Description styles */
        .description {
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            color: #95a5a6;
            line-height: 1.5;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
        }

        /* Button styles */
        .button {
            padding: 14px 28px;
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            background-color: #3498db;
            color: #fff;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 8px;
            cursor: pointer;
            text-decoration: none;
            display: inline-block;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
        }

        .button:hover {
            background-color: #2980b9;
        }

        .docs-button {
            background-color: #f39c12;
        }

        .docs-button:hover {
            background-color: #e67e22;
        }

        /* Footer styles */
        footer {
            margin-top: 30px;
            font-size: 0.85rem;
            color: #bdc3c7;
        }

        footer a {
            color: #3498db;
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        footer a:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }

        /* Media queries for responsiveness */
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .landing-container {
                padding: 30px;
            }

            h1 {
                font-size: 2.2rem;
            }

            h2 {
                font-size: 1.3rem;
            }

            .button {
                font-size: 1rem;
                padding: 12px 20px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="landing-container">
        <div class="logo">
            <img src="https://cdn.worldvectorlogo.com/logos/saml-1.svg" alt="SAML Logo">
        </div>
        <h1>SAML Provider</h1>
        <h2>Secure Single Sign-On & Identity Federation</h2>

        <p class="description">
            Manage and control secure access across your applications with SAML-based Single Sign-On (SSO).
            Explore the API documentation to integrate or start by logging in below.
        </p>

     
        <a href="/api/docs" class="button docs-button">SAML API Docs</a>

        <footer>
            <p>&copy; 2024 Blue-Bricks. All rights reserved.
            </p>
        </footer>
    </div>
</body>

</html>